title: undefined reference to `caffe2::ClipTransformRGB'
body_html:
hi ,all:
when I compile caffe2, an error appears:
/home/caffe2/framework/pytorch/build/lib/libcaffe2_gpu.so: undefined reference to `caffe2::ClipTransformRGB
the function is defined in './caffe2/video/video_io.h', I also add include_directories() in CMakeLists.txt file, but no effect.
what should I do please?
Thanks.
